  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>Floating within the shell is a haunting glow, a beacon both beautiful and cursed.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be <span class=\"name name-special\">gelatinous</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">spectral</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个有生命的、可生育的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已可孵化！</span><br><br>壳里萦绕着漂浮的光球，散发着美丽而具有诅咒气息的光辉。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-special\">凝胶状</span>以及<span class=\"name name-technology\">发光</span>的基因潜质。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">正準備孵化！</span><br><br>漂浮在殼內的是一隻令人難以忘懷的發光體，交織著美麗與受詛咒的氣息。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物從潛在基因看來，可能具有<span class=\"name name-special\">膠狀</span>且<span class=\"name name-technology\">光譜</span>的特徵。"
  },
